<div id="entry-56">
	<div class="entry-header">
		<h2 class="asset-name entry-title"><a href="../entry.php_a_2009_11_concordia-signs-igee-agreement.php">Concordia signs IGEE agreement</a></h2>
		<div class="entry-meta" title="2009-11-25T18:06:03-05:00">Wednesday Nov 25, 2009
                </div>
	</div>

	<div class="entry-content">
	
		<div class="entry-body">
			On Tuesday, November 24,<b> President Judith Woodsworth</b> signed the renewal of the agreement with the <b>Institut en Genie de l'Energie Electronique</b> (IGEE), of which <a class="zem_slink" href="http://www.concordia.ca/" title="Concordia University" rel="homepage">Concordia University</a> is a member.<br /><br />On hand for the signing were <b>Dr. Hoang Le-Huy</b>, Executive Director of the IGEE, as well as <b>Dr. Bill Lynch</b>, Concordia's representative on the IGEE Committee, and<b> Dean Robin Drew</b>.<br /><br /><a href="http://newsfeed.encs.concordia.ca/encs_test/IGEE_agreement.jpg"><img alt="IGEE agreement" src="http://newsfeed.encs.concordia.ca/encs_test/assets_c/2010/01/IGEE_agreement-thumb-440x330-77.jpg" class="mt-image-center" style="margin: 0pt auto 20px; text-align: center; display: block;" width="440" height="330" /></a>The other signing institutions are: <a class="zem_slink" href="http://www.polymtl.ca/en/" title="√0cole Polytechnique de Montr√©al" rel="homepage">√0cole polytechnique de Montr√©al</a>, <a class="zem_slink" href="http://etsmtl.ca/" title="√0cole de technologie sup√©rieure" rel="homepage">√0cole de technologie sup√©rieure</a>, <a class="zem_slink" href="http://www.ulaval.ca/" title="Universit√© Laval" rel="homepage">Universit√© Laval</a>, <a class="zem_slink" href="http://www.mcgill.ca/" title="McGill University" rel="homepage">McGill University</a>, <a class="zem_slink" href="http://www.usherbrooke.ca/" title="Universit√© de Sherbrooke" rel="homepage">Universit√© de Sherbrooke</a>, Universit√© de Qu√©bec √† Chicoutimi, <a class="zem_slink" href="http://www.uquebec.ca/" title="Universit√© du Qu√©bec" rel="homepage">Universit√© du Qu√©bec</a> √† Rimouski, Universit√© du Qu√©bec √† Trois Rivi√®res, and Institut en g√©nie de l'√©nergie √©lectrique.<br /><br />The IGEE's mission is to help train engineerse with a specialty in electrical engineering through industry partnerships. The organization's role is to facilitate collaboration and share resources between universities while allowing industry partners to become involved with the training of the next generation of electrical engineers.<br /><br />Hydro Qu√©bec is a proud sponsor of the program. For more on the IGEE, visit their official website.<br />


